It has been reported that a Nigerian man, Christian Onuoha, has been killed in a very painful manner in Umuahia. According to a witness simply identified as Amaka, the police officer identified as Collins Akpugo, allegedly shot the victim, Christian Onuoha, dead along the Okwulaga Afara-Ukwu, Ibeku, Umuahia, Abia state. Amaka revealed that the victim simply asked the policeman to dim his headlights. The officer then got angry and shot Onuoha dead.. The state police command is yet to react to the allegation. Source